<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Works</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><i><a href="/wiki/Parallel_Lives" title="Parallel Lives">Parallel Lives</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Moralia" title="Moralia">Moralia</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span></i> <a href="/wiki/Pseudo-Plutarch" title="Pseudo-Plutarch">Pseudo-Plutarch</a></div>
